{"segment_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0001", "section_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush", "source_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 1, "text_original": "禽子再拜再拜曰：", "text_normalized": "禽子再拜再拜曰：", "canonical_ref": "48.1", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0002", "section_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush", "source_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 2, "text_original": "「敢問適人強弱，遂以傅城，後上先斷，以為法程，斬城為基，掘下為室，前上不止，後射既疾，為之柰何？", "text_normalized": "「敢問適人強弱，遂以傅城，後上先斷，以為法程，斬城為基，掘下為室，前上不止，後射既疾，為之柰何？", "canonical_ref": "48.2", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0003", "section_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush", "source_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 3, "text_original": "」子墨子曰：", "text_normalized": "」子墨子曰：", "canonical_ref": "48.3", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0004", "section_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush", "source_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 4, "text_original": "「子問蛾傅之守邪？", "text_normalized": "「子問蛾傅之守邪？", "canonical_ref": "48.4", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0005", "section_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush", "source_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 5, "text_original": "蛾傅者，將之忿者也。", "text_normalized": "蛾傅者，將之忿者也。", "canonical_ref": "48.5", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0006", "section_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush", "source_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 6, "text_original": "守為行臨射之，校機藉之，擢之，太氾迫之，燒荅覆之，沙石雨之，然則蛾傅之攻敗矣。", "text_normalized": "守為行臨射之，校機藉之，擢之，太氾迫之，燒荅覆之，沙石雨之，然則蛾傅之攻敗矣。", "canonical_ref": "48.6", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0007", "section_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush", "source_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 7, "text_original": "備蛾傅為縣脾，以木板厚二寸，前後三尺，旁廣五尺，高五尺，而折為下磨車，轉徑尺六寸。", "text_normalized": "備蛾傅為縣脾，以木板厚二寸，前後三尺，旁廣五尺，高五尺，而折為下磨車，轉徑尺六寸。", "canonical_ref": "48.7", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0008", "section_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush", "source_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 8, "text_original": "令一人操二丈四方，刃其兩端，居縣脾中，以鐵璅敷縣二脾上衡，為之機，令有力四人下上之，弗離。", "text_normalized": "令一人操二丈四方，刃其兩端，居縣脾中，以鐵璅敷縣二脾上衡，為之機，令有力四人下上之，弗離。", "canonical_ref": "48.8", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0009", "section_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush", "source_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 9, "text_original": "施縣脾，大數二十步一，攻隊所在六步一。", "text_normalized": "施縣脾，大數二十步一，攻隊所在六步一。", "canonical_ref": "48.9", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0010", "section_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush", "source_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 10, "text_original": "為纍，荅廣從丈各二尺，以木為上衡，以麻索大編之，染其索塗中，為鐵璅，鉤其兩端之縣。", "text_normalized": "為纍，荅廣從丈各二尺，以木為上衡，以麻索大編之，染其索塗中，為鐵璅，鉤其兩端之縣。", "canonical_ref": "48.10", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0011", "section_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush", "source_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 11, "text_original": "客則蛾傅城，燒荅以覆之，連梃，抄大皆救之。", "text_normalized": "客則蛾傅城，燒荅以覆之，連梃，抄大皆救之。", "canonical_ref": "48.11", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0012", "section_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush", "source_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 12, "text_original": "以車兩走，軸閒廣大以圉，犯之。", "text_normalized": "以車兩走，軸閒廣大以圉，犯之。", "canonical_ref": "48.12", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0013", "section_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush", "source_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 13, "text_original": "刺其兩端。", "text_normalized": "刺其兩端。", "canonical_ref": "48.13", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0014", "section_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush", "source_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 14, "text_original": "以束輪，遍編塗其上。", "text_normalized": "以束輪，遍編塗其上。", "canonical_ref": "48.14", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0015", "section_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush", "source_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 15, "text_original": "室中以榆若蒸，以棘為旁，命曰火捽，一曰傳湯，以當隊。", "text_normalized": "室中以榆若蒸，以棘為旁，命曰火捽，一曰傳湯，以當隊。", "canonical_ref": "48.15", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0016", "section_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush", "source_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 16, "text_original": "客則乘隊，燒傳湯，斬維而下之，令勇士隨而擊之，以為勇士前行，城上輒塞壞城。", "text_normalized": "客則乘隊，燒傳湯，斬維而下之，令勇士隨而擊之，以為勇士前行，城上輒塞壞城。", "canonical_ref": "48.16", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0017", "section_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush", "source_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 17, "text_original": "城下足為下說鑱杙，長五尺，大圉半以上，皆剡其末，為五行，行閒廣三尺，貍三尺，大耳樹之。", "text_normalized": "城下足為下說鑱杙，長五尺，大圉半以上，皆剡其末，為五行，行閒廣三尺，貍三尺，大耳樹之。", "canonical_ref": "48.17", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0018", "section_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush", "source_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 18, "text_original": "為連殳，長五尺，大十尺。", "text_normalized": "為連殳，長五尺，大十尺。", "canonical_ref": "48.18", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0019", "section_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush", "source_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 19, "text_original": "梃長二尺，大六寸，索長二尺。", "text_normalized": "梃長二尺，大六寸，索長二尺。", "canonical_ref": "48.19", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0020", "section_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush", "source_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 20, "text_original": "椎，柄長六尺，首長尺五寸。", "text_normalized": "椎，柄長六尺，首長尺五寸。", "canonical_ref": "48.20", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0021", "section_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush", "source_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 21, "text_original": "斧，柄長六尺，刃必利，皆築其一後。", "text_normalized": "斧，柄長六尺，刃必利，皆築其一後。", "canonical_ref": "48.21", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0022", "section_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush", "source_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 22, "text_original": "荅廣丈二尺，其長丈六尺，垂前衡四寸，兩端接尺相覆，勿令魚鱗槮，著其後行。", "text_normalized": "荅廣丈二尺，其長丈六尺，垂前衡四寸，兩端接尺相覆，勿令魚鱗槮，著其後行。", "canonical_ref": "48.22", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0023", "section_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush", "source_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 23, "text_original": "中央木繩一，長二丈六尺，荅樓不會者以牒塞，數暴乾，荅為格，令風上下。", "text_normalized": "中央木繩一，長二丈六尺，荅樓不會者以牒塞，數暴乾，荅為格，令風上下。", "canonical_ref": "48.23", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0024", "section_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush", "source_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 24, "text_original": "堞惡疑壞者，先貍木十尺一枚一，節壞，鄧植以押慮盧薄於木，盧薄表八尺，廣七寸，經尺一，數施一擊而下之，為上下釫而斫之。", "text_normalized": "堞惡疑壞者，先貍木十尺一枚一，節壞，鄧植以押慮盧薄於木，盧薄表八尺，廣七寸，經尺一，數施一擊而下之，為上下釫而斫之。", "canonical_ref": "48.24", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0025", "section_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush", "source_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 25, "text_original": "經一鈞、禾樓、羅石、縣荅，植內毋植外。", "text_normalized": "經一鈞、禾樓、羅石、縣荅，植內毋植外。", "canonical_ref": "48.25", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0026", "section_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush", "source_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 26, "text_original": "杜格，貍四尺，高者十丈，木長短相雜，兌其上，而外內厚塗之。", "text_normalized": "杜格，貍四尺，高者十丈，木長短相雜，兌其上，而外內厚塗之。", "canonical_ref": "48.26", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0027", "section_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush", "source_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 27, "text_original": "為前行行棧、縣荅。", "text_normalized": "為前行行棧、縣荅。", "canonical_ref": "48.27", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0028", "section_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush", "source_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 28, "text_original": "隅為樓，樓必曲裡。", "text_normalized": "隅為樓，樓必曲裡。", "canonical_ref": "48.28", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0029", "section_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush", "source_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 29, "text_original": "土五步一，毋其二十畾。", "text_normalized": "土五步一，毋其二十畾。", "canonical_ref": "48.29", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0030", "section_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush", "source_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 30, "text_original": "雀穴十尺一，下堞三尺，廣其外。", "text_normalized": "雀穴十尺一，下堞三尺，廣其外。", "canonical_ref": "48.30", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0031", "section_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush", "source_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 31, "text_original": "轉傅城上，樓及散與池革盆。", "text_normalized": "轉傅城上，樓及散與池革盆。", "canonical_ref": "48.31", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0032", "section_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush", "source_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 32, "text_original": "若轉，攻卒擊其後，煖失治。", "text_normalized": "若轉，攻卒擊其後，煖失治。", "canonical_ref": "48.32", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0033", "section_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush", "source_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 33, "text_original": "車革火。", "text_normalized": "車革火。", "canonical_ref": "48.33", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0034", "section_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush", "source_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 34, "text_original": "凡殺蛾傅而攻者之法，置薄城外，去城十尺，薄厚十尺。", "text_normalized": "凡殺蛾傅而攻者之法，置薄城外，去城十尺，薄厚十尺。", "canonical_ref": "48.34", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0035", "section_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush", "source_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 35, "text_original": "伐操之法，大小盡木斷之，以十尺為斷，離而深貍堅築之，毋使可拔。", "text_normalized": "伐操之法，大小盡木斷之，以十尺為斷，離而深貍堅築之，毋使可拔。", "canonical_ref": "48.35", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0036", "section_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush", "source_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 36, "text_original": "二十步一殺，有鬲，厚十尺。", "text_normalized": "二十步一殺，有鬲，厚十尺。", "canonical_ref": "48.36", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0037", "section_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush", "source_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 37, "text_original": "殺有兩門，門廣五步，薄門板梯貍之，勿築，令易拔。", "text_normalized": "殺有兩門，門廣五步，薄門板梯貍之，勿築，令易拔。", "canonical_ref": "48.37", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0038", "section_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush", "source_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 38, "text_original": "城上希薄門而置搗。", "text_normalized": "城上希薄門而置搗。", "canonical_ref": "48.38", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0039", "section_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush", "source_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 39, "text_original": "縣火，四尺一椅，五步一灶，灶門有爐炭。", "text_normalized": "縣火，四尺一椅，五步一灶，灶門有爐炭。", "canonical_ref": "48.39", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0040", "section_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush", "source_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 40, "text_original": "傳令敵人盡入，車火燒門，縣火次之，出載而立，其廣終隊，兩載之間一火，皆立而待鼓音而然，即俱發之。", "text_normalized": "傳令敵人盡入，車火燒門，縣火次之，出載而立，其廣終隊，兩載之間一火，皆立而待鼓音而然，即俱發之。", "canonical_ref": "48.40", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0041", "section_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush", "source_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 41, "text_original": "敵人辟火而復攻，縣火復下，敵人甚病。", "text_normalized": "敵人辟火而復攻，縣火復下，敵人甚病。", "canonical_ref": "48.41", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0042", "section_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush", "source_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 42, "text_original": "敵引哭而榆，則令吾死士左右出穴門擊遺師，令賁士、主將皆聽城鼓之音而出，又聽城鼓之音而入。", "text_normalized": "敵引哭而榆，則令吾死士左右出穴門擊遺師，令賁士、主將皆聽城鼓之音而出，又聽城鼓之音而入。", "canonical_ref": "48.42", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0043", "section_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush", "source_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 43, "text_original": "因素出兵將施伏，夜半，而城上四面鼓噪，敵人必或，破軍殺將。", "text_normalized": "因素出兵將施伏，夜半，而城上四面鼓噪，敵人必或，破軍殺將。", "canonical_ref": "48.43", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0044", "section_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush", "source_id": "mozi-048-defence-against-ant-rush__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 44, "text_original": "以白衣為服，以號相得。", "text_normalized": "以白衣為服，以號相得。", "canonical_ref": "48.44", "notes": ""}
